# Security Gateway — protect raw security/abuse logs (redacted-only, no raw IP/PII)
data/security-gateway*.json
data/security-events*.json
artifacts/*security-raw*
artifacts/*abuse-raw*
security-exports/private/
*.security.raw.json
*.abuse.raw.json

# Tenant Isolation — protect raw tenant/leak reports (redacted-only, no full PII)
data/tenant-isolation*.json
artifacts/*tenant-isolation-raw*
artifacts/*leak-raw*
tenant-isolation-exports/private/
*.tenant.raw.json
*.leak.raw.json
